{"tid":1177904,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為二手P30低至港幣約千元","createTime":"2019-05-30T05:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T06:56:49.000Z","uid":126320,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"42161c3a7e81381033375f2b29aec7c29b242b27","tid":1177904,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"對華為（Huawei）不利的消息一浪接一浪，導致好些人都不看好華為手機的前景。據外國媒體報道，在英國的二手手機巿場，華為的售價暴跌，其中如 P30 Pro 的售價，僅餘 100 英鎊左右（約 1000 港元），2018 上半年推出 P20 Pro，則跌至 50 英鎊（約 500 港元），跟原價相比，跌幅超過 90%。<br />\n<br />\n【科技】Huawei P30 Pro/Mate X 旗艦被 Google 正式除名！？【封殺華為】<br />\n<br />\n華為早前推出的新款旗艦機 P30 Pro，本來評價算不俗，不過近期連番不利的消息，無疑對市場消費環境造成影響。據英國《每日快報》（Daily Express）報道，華為在英國的二手機巿場，售價暴跌，才推出不久的  P30 Pro，現時大概只售 100 英鎊，而 Samsung S10 128GB 版本則維持在 455 英鎊。至於 P20 Pro 則更誇張，之前的二手價尚有  280 英鎊，但如今跌至只有 50 英鎊，而同期的 Samsung S9 則維持 235 英鎊，可見華為手機的跌幅，明顯比其他品牌誇張。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，二手商對於華為機型的前景不看好，憂慮手機不容易賣出去，並反映在二手價格上，類似情況亦有在星加坡出現。至於香港方面，在網絡有人開價 1200-1800 港元左右收購 P30 Pro，但放售的人暫時似乎不多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2359634/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%20P20%20Pro%EF%BC%8FP30%20Pro%20%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%B9%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%86%82%E8%AE%8A%E5%BB%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%85%E4%B8%80%E6%8A%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2359634%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%2520P20%2520Pro%25EF%25BC%258FP30%2520Pro%2520%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25B7%258C%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%2586%2582%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%258A%2598&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuiclKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=5ebfced2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2359634/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%20P20%20Pro%EF%BC%8FP30%20Pro%20%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%B9%E6%9A%B4%E8%B7%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%86%82%E8%AE%8A%E5%BB%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%83%85%E4%B8%80%E6%8A%98</a><br />\n<br />\n香港邊度有華為平貨執???<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千元就有,真係點計都係抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b2e88b70d9f9c3a60fbb545c0cb651981c3e63","tid":1177904,"uid":12015,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:06:59.000Z","msg":"一千蚊買舊磚返屋企扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb6689f0b5fc20b2e824ef6ca163a51063f18d8","tid":1177904,"uid":222712,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"點解我唔去地盤問下師父有冇磚頭唔要"},{"pid":"dcf1cfd871e4ad4eb4bdf992dbf27c80cc81a8c4","tid":1177904,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"$1000 抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc361388aa14da82893fd9015586cdc85376829","tid":1177904,"uid":76421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"1000一定買部黎玩下"},{"pid":"bd567791646c6c39c939a4ecba768caf8054ddb4","tid":1177904,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"支那狗一定All in 啦<br />\n支那一亮劍部野即刻反彈"},{"pid":"d322af633fe6bfb4cc7f1f68b1c252c2563f01ab","tid":1177904,"uid":77143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"邊度有100鎊p30 pro 買？<br />\n買部翻黎當望遠鏡都好"},{"pid":"79e3993fe64b3d4e76f371710914e9abdad2cc63","tid":1177904,"uid":39527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d322af633fe6bfb4cc7f1f68b1c252c2563f01ab","tid":1177904,"uid":77143,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"邊度有100鎊p30 pro 買？<br />\n買部翻黎當望遠鏡都好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"望遠鏡要成千蚊?"},{"pid":"225dfae3f32b37b8f7a9d527d6d06d3a95f2b007","tid":1177904,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"買舊磚<img src=\"